    <item>
      <title>拜登将与普京一起庆祝诺曼底登陆 80 周年，特朗普谴责</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/d-day-80th-anniversary-lets-biden-rebuke-trump-putin</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登将与他所认为的当今对民主构成威胁的两位人物——弗拉基米尔·普京和唐纳德·特朗普——展开对决，这是美国在反对威权主义方面取得的最伟大胜利之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/d-day-80th-anniversary-lets-biden-rebuke-trump-putin</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普称共和党的堕胎言论伤害了他的政党</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/trump-says-republican-abortion-rhetoric-hurts-his-party</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普表示，共和党有关堕胎限制的言论已经损害了该党的利益，凸显了这一缺陷导致共和党在 2022 年中期国会选举中的胜利低于预期，并有可能成为 11 月的拖累。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/trump-says-republican-abortion-rhetoric-hurts-his-party</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 03:30:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国强烈谴责金正恩投放垃圾气球等挑衅行为</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/south-korea-slams-kim-s-provocations-including-trash-balloons</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国总统尹锡烈表示，朝鲜向边境地区运送垃圾的气球应该感到羞耻，并加大了对金正恩政权的压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/south-korea-slams-kim-s-provocations-including-trash-balloons</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 03:01:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
